import React from "react"; export default function Experience() { return (
Experiences

Competitions

NUS Medical Grand Challenge 2023

Aug 2023

Finalist

Proposed HindSight, an anonymous, accurate and convenient application that allows users to screen for anal-related illnesses through an image-based disease detection model designed by local startup HeHealth.

Singapore Airlines App Challenge 2023

Jul 2023

2nd Runners-Up

Created SIA Concierge, a generative-AI based itinerary planner encompassing SIA's flights, hotels and Pelago. Achieved 3rd out of over 280 local and international teams.

Chulalongkorn International Business Case Competition 2023

May 2023

1st Runners-Up

Proposed an advertising campaign for a health and wellness company in Bangkok (8hrs) as well as a Sustainability Master Plan for the Phuket Government (24hrs). Achieved 2nd from the best casing teams from across the world.

Credit Agricole X NTU Earthlink Sustainable Finance Case Competition 2023

Mar 2023

Champion

Proposed adoption of Hydrogen Direct Reduction Iron (H-DRI) for a ASEAN Steelmaker to achieve sustainable goals. Proposed a multi-phase implementation to work around technology and financial constraints in the sector.

Circles Life Case Competition 2023

Dec 2022

1st Runners-Up

Provided innovative solutions to improve competitiveness in the telco industry by targeting new customer audiences and customer retention.

Shopee Product and Design Challenge 2022

Oct 2022

Champion

Emerged champion amongst over 600 local open category teams , with our UI/UX suggestions to optimised the user funnel to increase userbase and customer loyalty.

Work Experience

Associate

NTU Business Solutions Case Club

Since Sep 2022

Premier business case club representing the school in local and international case competitions against top business schools around the world. Held role of Training Director, training associates fundamental casing skills and case teams for International Competitions..

Nominee Director

SCB Corporate

Since Jun 2022

Along with my partners from Sri Lanka, we provide accounting and auditing services for companies around the world. We utilize our expert accountants in Sri Lanka to provide personalized services for our clients.

Sales and Operations Executive

Focus Rentals

Since Sep 2022

Pitched and sold car rental packages to Private Hire Drivers and assisted in operations aspects of car rental industry

); }
